        For example in <xref ref="problem-maybegroups"/> describes <m>S_3</m> at the end.
      </p>
    </introduction>
    <task>
      <statement>
        <p>
          Pick 3 different <m>n</m>'s at least 2.  Show that <m>S_n</m> for your choices for a group.
        </p>
      </statement>
    </task>
    <task>
